            <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Problem: Automatic copy to clipboard doesn’t work&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When ssh’d to a remote server&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Running &lt;code&gt;tmux&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;From a Ghostty terminal window&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But does work:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When not running &lt;code&gt;tmux&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;, everything else the same.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Solution:
On the remote server, update `~&#x2F;.tmux.conf and add the line:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;plain&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g allow-passthrough on&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;References:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;anomalyco&#x2F;opencode&#x2F;issues&#x2F;4283#issuecomment-3909686321&quot;&gt;GitHub Issue&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
</content>
